=<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Tailored Resume – {{ $json.jobRoleEcho }}</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif; background: #0d1117; color: #c9d1d9; min-height: 100vh; }

    /* Header */
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1f2e 0%, #16213e 50%, #0f3460 100%);
      border-bottom: 1px solid #30363d;
      padding: 28px 40px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .header-icon { font-size: 36px; }
    .header-title { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #f0f6fc; }
    .header-sub { font-size: 13px; color: #8b949e; margin-top: 4px; }
    .badge-row { display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-top: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .badge {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px;
      padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600;
    }
    .badge-green  { background: #1a4731; color: #3fb950; border: 1px solid #238636; }
    .badge-blue   { background: #1c2d50; color: #79c0ff; border: 1px solid #1f6feb; }
    .badge-purple { background: #2d1b69; color: #d2a8ff; border: 1px solid #6e40c9; }
    .badge-orange { background: #3d2200; color: #ffa657; border: 1px solid #9e6a03; }

    /* Main layout */
    .container { max-width: 960px; margin: 32px auto; padding: 0 24px 60px; }

    /* Stats bar */
    .stats-bar {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .stat-card {
      background: #161b22;
      border: 1px solid #30363d;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 14px 18px;
    }
    .stat-label { font-size: 11px; color: #8b949e; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.8px; }
    .stat-value { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: #f0f6fc; margin-top: 4px; }

    /* Toolbar */
    .toolbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      background: #161b22;
      border: 1px solid #30363d;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
      padding: 12px 20px;
    }
    .toolbar-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #8b949e; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; }
    .btn-row { display: flex; gap: 8px; }
    .btn {
      padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid;
      font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.15s;
    }
    .btn-copy  { background: #21262d; color: #79c0ff; border-color: #30363d; }
    .btn-copy:hover  { background: #30363d; }
    .btn-print { background: #238636; color: #fff;    border-color: #2ea043; }
    .btn-print:hover { background: #2ea043; }

    /* Resume box */
    .resume-box {
      background: #0d1117;
      border: 1px solid #30363d;
      border-top: none;
      border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
      padding: 32px 36px;
    }
    .resume-content {
      font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
      font-size: 13.2px;
      line-height: 1.85;
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      word-break: break-word;
      color: #e6edf3;
    }

    /* Tips card */
    .tips-card {
      background: #161b22;
      border: 1px solid #30363d;
      border-left: 3px solid #3fb950;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 18px 22px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #8b949e;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .tips-card strong { color: #f0f6fc; }

    /* Footer */
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 24px;
      color: #484f58;
      font-size: 12px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    @media print {
      body { background: white; color: black; }
      .header, .stats-bar, .toolbar, .tips-card, footer { display: none; }
      .resume-box { border: none; padding: 0; }
      .resume-content { color: black; font-size: 12px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="header">
    <div class="header-icon">✨</div>
    <div>
      <div class="header-title">Resume Tailored Successfully</div>
      <div class="header-sub">Role: <strong style="color:#79c0ff">{{ $json.jobRoleEcho }}</strong></div>
      <div class="badge-row">
        <span class="badge badge-green">✅ Done</span>
        <span class="badge badge-purple">🤖 Mistral via Ollama</span>
        <span class="badge badge-blue">⚡ Local AI – 100% Private</span>
        <span class="badge badge-orange">⏱ {{ $json.evalDuration }}s generation</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">

    <div class="stats-bar">
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-label">Model</div>
        <div class="stat-value">{{ $json.modelUsed }}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-label">Target Role</div>
        <div class="stat-value" style="font-size:13px">{{ $json.jobRoleEcho }}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-label">Generation Time</div>
        <div class="stat-value">{{ $json.evalDuration }}s</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-label">Privacy</div>
        <div class="stat-value" style="color:#3fb950">100% Local</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="toolbar">
      <span class="toolbar-title">📄 Your Tailored Resume</span>
      <div class="btn-row">
        <button class="btn btn-copy" onclick="copyResume()">📋 Copy Text</button>
        <button class="btn btn-print" onclick="window.print()">🖨 Print / Save PDF</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="resume-box">
      <div class="resume-content" id="resumeText">{{ $json.tailoredResume }}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="tips-card">
      <strong>💡 Next Steps:</strong><br>
      1. Review the <strong>TAILORING NOTES</strong> section at the bottom of the resume above.<br>
      2. Click <strong>Print / Save PDF</strong> to export a clean ATS-ready PDF.<br>
      3. Double-check GitHub/LinkedIn links before submitting.<br>
      4. Run it through <strong>jobscan.co</strong> to verify ATS keyword score.
    </div>

  </div>

  <footer>Avinash Resume Tailor • Powered by Mistral via Ollama • 100% Local & Private • n8n Workflow</footer>

  <script>
    function copyResume() {
      const text = document.getElementById('resumeText').innerText;
      navigator.clipboard.writeText(text).then(() => {
        const btn = document.querySelector('.btn-copy');
        btn.textContent = '✅ Copied!';
        setTimeout(() => btn.textContent = '📋 Copy Text', 2500);
      });
    }
  </script>

</body>
</html>
